#!/usr/bin/env testml


*jsc.validate(*json) == *valid


=== Test 1 - maxProperties validation - shorter is valid
--- valid: true
--- jsc
{"maxProperties": 2}
--- json
{"foo": 1}


=== Test 2 - maxProperties validation - exact length is valid
--- valid: true
--- ^jsc
--- json
{"foo": 1, "bar": 2}


=== Test 3 - maxProperties validation - too long is invalid
--- valid: false
--- ^jsc
--- json
{"foo": 1, "bar": 2, "baz": 3}


=== Test 4 - maxProperties validation - ignores arrays
--- valid: true
--- ^jsc
--- json
[1, 2, 3]


=== Test 5 - maxProperties validation - ignores strings
--- valid: true
--- ^jsc
--- json
"foobar"


=== Test 6 - maxProperties validation - ignores other non-objects
--- valid: true
--- ^jsc
--- json
12


